             was indicted for <rs id="t17890422-51-off220" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17890422-51-off220" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17890422-51-off220" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t17890422-51-cd221" type="crimeDate">28th of February</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17890422-51-off220 t17890422-51-cd221"></join>, a linen sheet, value 2 s. a pair of blankets, value 2 s. and a rug, value 12 d.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17890422-51-victim468" type="victimName">
                     Thomas 
                     Isaacs
                  <interp inst="t17890422-51-victim468" type="surname" value="Isaacs"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17890422-51-victim468" type="given" value="Thomas"></interp>
